      "description": "The Equable Shares Hedged Equity ETF (HEDG) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in large cap equity. The fund is an actively managed fund-of-funds that seeks income, risk mitigation and long-term capital appreciation through a covered call options writing strategy. The fund provides US large-cap equity exposure through one or more ETFs, while writing exchange traded call options on the same securities. HEDG was launched on Oct 13, 2025 and is issued by Equable.",
